( Initializes the readln subsystem )
: RDLN$
    ( 53 == rdln's memory )
    H@ 0x53 RAM+ !
    ( 2 for IN>, plus 2 for extra bytes after buffer: 1 for
      the last typed 0x0a and one for the following NULL. )
    INBUFSZ 4 + ALLOT
    (infl)
    ['] RDLN< 0x0c RAM+ !
    1 0x06 RAM+ !  ( 06 == C<? )
;

